---

<section id="kontakt" class="section contact-section" aria-labelledby="contact-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 id="contact-heading">Kontaktieren Sie uns</h2>
      <p>Wir beraten Sie gerne zu Ihren Anforderungen im Bereich Cybersicherheit.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="form-wrapper" role="region" aria-label="Kontaktformular">
      <iframe
        src="https://app.formbricks.com/s/mb6n4ud3uoqvl0n2jx5us1fl?embed=true"
        title="Kontaktformular"
        aria-label="Kontaktformular"
        loading="lazy"
        referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
      ></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .contact-section {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .form-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    height: 80dvh;
    max-height: 700px;
    overflow: auto;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  iframe {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: 0;
  }
</style>
